expert guide explores the physics of pet travel safety, the rise of 'Smart Cages' with biometric sensors, and the latest global regulations for keeping your canine companion secure on the road.\",\n  \"image\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/4df06fbcc0523374e338628abbd73934fe209066-1024x1024.webp?w=1200\",\n      \"width\": 1024,\n      \"height\": 1024\n    }\n  ],\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-01-20T14:49:12.684Z\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-01-20T15:30:09Z\",\n  \"author\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Person\",\n    \"name\": \"Mahendra Balal\",\n    \"image\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/fe569ca7a7aea456e6d846511889756220b0ff98-1029x579.jpg?rect=226,0,579,579&w=96&h=96\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"Mahendra is a professional pet-specific content writer.\"\n  },\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Indoor Dog Park\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.indoordogpark.org/images/logo/logo.png\",\n      \"width\": 200,\n      \"height\": 60\n    },\n    \"url\": \"https://www.indoordogpark.org\"\n  },\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://www.indoordogpark.org/blog/dog-cages-in-cars-safety-smart-tech-and-legal-standards\"\n  },\n  \"url\": \"https://www.indoordogpark.org/blog/dog-cages-in-cars-safety-smart-tech-and-legal-standards\",\n  \"wordCount\": 1515,\n  \"timeRequired\": \"PT8M\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en-US\",\n  \"isPartOf\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Blog\",\n    \"name\": \"Indoor Dog Park Blog\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.indoordogpark.org/blog\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": \"Dog Daycare, indoor dog park, Climate control, indoor dog park, indoor dog parks, dog parks, California, dog friendly, pet care, dog training\",\n  \"articleSection\": [\n    \"Dog Daycare\",\n    \"indoor dog park\"\n  ]\