-for-a-5-minute-drive-to-the-indoor-dog-park\",\"title\":\"Q: Do I need a cage for a 5-minute drive to the Indoor Dog Park?\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"9-future-trends-toward-level-5-autonomous-pet-travel\",\"title\":\"9. Future Trends: Toward \\\"Level 5\\\" Autonomous Pet Travel\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"10-the-expert-verdict-safety-is-not-a-luxury\",\"title\":\"10. The Expert Verdict: Safety is Not a Luxury\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"cited-sources-research\",\"title\":\"Cited Sources & Research\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"elite-heavy-duty-crash-tested-pet-crate\",\"title\":\"Elite Heavy-Duty Crash-Tested Pet Crate\",\"level\":3}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Follow Us\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Stay updated with the latest indoor dog park news and tips!\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://x.com/Indoordogp40934\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on X (Twitter)\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-twitter\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"X (Twitter)\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.facebook.com/IndoorDogParkDirectory\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\",\"aria-label\":\"Follow us on Facebook\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-facebook\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Facebook\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.instagram.com/indoordogpark2025/