2. 7 Reasons Why a Crash-Tested Cage is Mandatory in 2026\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"3-the-rise-of-smart-cages-the-tech-revolution\",\"title\":\"3. The Rise of \\\"Smart\\\" Cages: The Tech Revolution\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"integrated-environmental-monitoring\",\"title\":\"Integrated Environmental Monitoring\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"smart-materials\",\"title\":\"Smart Materials\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"4-comparing-the-best-2026-market-leaders\",\"title\":\"4. Comparing the Best: 2026 Market Leaders\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"5-the-2026-legal-landscape-where-you-need-a-cage\",\"title\":\"5. The 2026 Legal Landscape: Where You Need a Cage\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"6-training-your-dog-for-car-cage-success\",\"title\":\"6. Training Your Dog for Car Cage Success\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"7-cages-vs-alternatives-the-venn-diagram-of-choice\",\"title\":\"7. Cages vs. Alternatives: The Venn Diagram of Choice\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"8-frequent-questions-from-our-community\",\"title\":\"8. Frequent Questions From Our Community\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"q-are-soft-sided-fabric-crates-safe-for-car-travel\",\"title\":\"Q: Are soft-sided \\\"fabric\\\" crates safe for car travel?\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"q-can-i-put-two-dogs-in-one-car-cage\",\"title\":\"Q: Can I put two dogs in one car cage?\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"q-do-i-need-a-cage-for-a-5-minute-drive-to-the-indoor-dog-park\",\"title\":\"Q: Do I need a cage for a 5-minute drive to the Indoor Dog Park?\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"9-future-trends-toward-level-5-autonomous-pet-travel\",\"title\":\"9. Future Trends: Toward \\\"Level 5\\\" Autonomous Pet Travel\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"10-the-expert-verdict-safety-is-not-a-luxury\",\"title\":\"10. The Expert Verdict: Safety is Not a Luxury\",\"level\":2},{\"id\":\"cited-sources-research\",\"title\":\"Cited Sources & Research\",\"level\":3},{\"id\":\"elite-heavy-duty-crash-tested-pet-crate\",\"title\":\"Elite Heavy-Duty Crash-Tested Pet Crate\",\"level\":3}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"class